:拉佩斯形容自己扮演的这个考古学家对神的信仰非常强烈，并称“电影中途发生了许多事情，她变成了一个战士，到了最后，她又成了唯一的幸存者”<ref name="colliderrapaceinterview">{{cite web |url=http://collider.com/noomi-rapace-sherlock-holmes-2-prometheus-interview/132137/ |title=Noomi Rapace Talks 'Sherlock Holmes: A Game of Shadows', 'Prometheus', and 'Dead Man Down' |last=Radish |first=Christina |publisher=Collider.com |date=2011-12-14 |accessdate=2013-12-25 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68TIEKAS5?url=http://collider.com/noomi-rapace-sherlock-holmes-2-prometheus-interview/132137/ |archivedate=2012-06-16 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。 为了辅助自己的[[方法演技|方法演技]]，她给肖制定了一套完整的背景故事<ref name="CastRapace6">{{cite web |first=Fred |last=Topel |title=Noomi Rapace on 'Sherlock,' 'Prometheus' and 'Dragon Tattoo' |url=http://www.craveonline.com/film/interviews/179711-noomi-rapace-on-sherlock-holmes-prometheus-and-dragon-tattoo |publisher=CraveOnline |date=2011-12-14 |accessdate=2013-12-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130602031056/http://www.craveonline.com/film/interviews/179711-noomi-rapace-on-sherlock-holmes-prometheus-and-dragon-tattoo |archivedate=2013-06-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，并与一位方言教练合作来练习英国口音<ref name="Hewitt">{{cite journal |last1=Hewitt |first1=Chris |title=Why Are We Here? |journal=Empire |issue= |page=|publisher= Bauer Media Group|date=2012年5月}}</ref>{{rp|64}}。她还请自己的化妆师在拍摄期间给自己的妆中增加额外的血迹和汗迹，让角色更加真实可信<ref name="CastRapace10">{{cite web |first= |last= |title=Noomi Rapace – Noomi Rapace Shocked Make-Up Artist With Blood And Sweat Request |url=http://www.contactmusic.com/news/noomi-rapace-shocked-make-up-artist-with-blood-and-sweat-request_1327349 |publisher=Contactmusic.com |date=2012-05-11 |accessdate=2013-05-28 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130528143706/http://www.contactmusic.com/news/noomi-rapace-shocked-make-up-artist-with-blood-and-sweat-request_1327349 | archivedate=2013-05-28 |deadurl=yes}}</ref>。拉佩斯说：“我们在那里拍摄了差不多六个月，真是超级紧张，我身上有时候会觉得很痛，但这个过程又实在是棒级了。”<ref name="Filming9">{{cite news |url=http://www.independent.ie/entertainment/movies/rapace-prometheus-was-so-intense-26802770.html |title=Rapace: Prometheus was so intense |date=2011-12-15 |accessdate=2013-12-25 |work=Irish Independent |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68TNdBsdt?url=http://www.independent.ie/entertainment/film-cinema/rapace-prometheus-was-so-intense-2965606.html |archivedate=2012-06-16 |deadurl=no }}</ref>她拒绝把自己的角色与《异形》系列中的埃伦·里普利（{{lang|en|Ellen Ripley}}）相比较<ref name="CastRapace5">{{cite web |first=Josh |last=Wigler | url=http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2011/03/07/prometheus-noomi-rapace-interview/ | title='Prometheus' Star Noomi Rapace Reveals 'Alien' Connection, Compares Her Character With Ripley | date=2011-03-07 | publisher=Viacom |work=MTV | accessdate=2013-12-25 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130510195522/http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2011/03/07/prometheus-noomi-rapace-interview/ | archivedate=2013-05-10 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。拉佩斯是在出演了2009年的电影《[[龙纹身的女孩_(2009年电影)|龙纹身的女孩]]》后引起了导演雷德利·斯科特的注意，两人在2010年8月进行了会面<ref name="CastRapace1">{{cite web | url=http://www.scriptflags.com/2010/08/noomi-rapace-girl-with-dragon-tattoo.html | title=Noomie Rapace (The Girl With The Dragon Tatoo) For Alien Prequel? | date=2010-08-20 | publisher=Script Flags | accessdate=2013-12-25 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20120616075312/http://www.scriptflags.com/2010/08/noomi-rapace-girl-with-dragon-tattoo.html | archivedate=2012-06-16 |deadurl=no}}</ref>，她的角色在2011年1月确定<ref name="Cast1">{{cite news|last=Finke |first=Nikki |url=http://www.deadline.com/2011/01/ridley-scott-directing-prometheus-for-fox-noomi-rapace-locked-while-angelina-jolie-and-charlize-theron-circling-2nd-female-lead/ |title=Ridley Scott Directing 'Prometheus' For Fox; Noomi Rapace Locked While Angelina Jolie And Charlize Theron Circling; Damon Lindelof Scripted With Scott From 'Alien' DNA |publisher=Deadline.com |date=2011-01-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131103201120/http://www.deadline.com/2011/01/ridley-scott-directing-prometheus-for-fox-noomi-rapace-locked-while-angelina-jolie-and-charlize-theron-circling-2nd-female-lead/ |archivedate=2013-11-03 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。电影开发过程中，另外几位[[女演员|女演员]]，[[安妮·海瑟薇|安妮·海瑟薇]]、[[娜塔莉·波特曼|娜塔莉·波特曼]]、[[杰玛·阿特登|杰玛·阿特登]]、[[嘉莉·慕萊根|嘉莉·慕萊根]]和[[艾比·考尼什|艾比·考尼什]]都曾是这个角色的考虑人选<ref name="CastRapace2">{{cite news | url=http://www.vulture.com/2010/10/fox_flips_for_damon_lindelofs.html | title=Fox Flips for Damon Lindelof's ''Alien'' Prequel Script, Wants Natalie Portman to Star | work=New York | date=2010-10-12 | accessdate=2013-12-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131220043622/http://www.vulture.com/2010/10/fox_flips_for_damon_lindelofs.html | archivedate=2013-12-20 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="CastRapace3">{{cite web | url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=69595#ixzz0yl5aMidG | title=Update: Gemma Arterton Meeting for Ridley Scott's Alien Prequels? | date=2010-09-06 | publisher=Coming Soon | accessdate=2013-12-25 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130723034015/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=69595#ixzz0yl5aMidG | archivedate=2013-07-23 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="CastRapace4">{{cite news | last=Fleming | first=Mike | url=http://www.deadline.com/2010/10/next-hot-female-role-noomi-rapace-in-hunt-for-ridley-scotts-3d-alien-prequel/ | title=Next Hot Female Role: Noomi Rapace In Hunt For Ridley Scott's 3D 'Alien' Prequel | publisher=Deadline New York | date=2010-10-07 | accessdate=2013-12-25 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20121011003320/http://www.deadline.com/2010/10/next-hot-female-role-noomi-rapace-in-hunt-for-ridley-scotts-3d-alien-prequel/ |archivedate=2012-10-11 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。出生于2003年的[[露西·哈钦森|露西·哈钦森]]（{{lang|en|Lucy Hutchinson}}）在片中扮演童年时代的肖<ref name="Lucy">{{cite news |last=Williamson |first=Hannah |url=http://www.yourlocalguardian.co.uk/news/local/croydonnews/9695061.Schoolgirl_stars_in_sci_fi_blockbuster/ |title=School Girl Stars in Sci-Fi Blockbuster |publisher=Newsquest Digital |work=Your Local Guardian |date=2012-05-09 |accessdate=2013-12-25 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68TNjgAJW?url=http://www.yourlocalguardian.co.uk/news/local/croydonnews/9695061.Schoolgirl_stars_in_sci_fi_blockbuster/ |archivedate=2012-06-16 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。
*[[麥可·法斯賓達|米高·法斯賓達]] 饰 大卫：
:大卫是一个人形机器人，是飞船上的管家兼维修员。它看起来和人类非常相似，并且开始发展出“自我、不安全感、嫉妒和羡慕”<ref name="paradise found">{{cite news |accessdate=2013-12-25 |archivedate=2012-10-23 |url=http://www.vulture.com/2010/12/paradise_found_ridley_scotts_a.html | title=Paradise Found: Ridley Scott’s Alien Prequel Gets a Title, Takes Aim at Yeoh and Fassbender | work=New York | date=2010-12-08 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023020840/http://www.vulture.com/2010/12/paradise_found_ridley_scotts_a.html |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="MiscWonderCon12">{{cite web |first= Christina |last=Radish |title=Director Ridley Scott, Writer Damon Lindelof and Michael Fassbender Talk Prometheus at WonderCon 2012 |url=http://collider.com/ridley-scott-damon-lindelof-michael-fassbender-prometheus-interview/153243/ | publisher=Collider.com |date=2012-03-18 |accessdate=2013-12-25 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131111065704/http://collider.com/ridley-scott-damon-lindelof-michael-fassbender-prometheus-interview/153243/ |archivedate=2013-11-11 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。编剧戴蒙·林道夫表示，这个角色提供了一个非人类的视角来看待片中发生的事情。他说：“从一个机器人的眼里看来，这是部什么样的电影？如果你问他：‘你对这一切都怎么看？发生了什么事？你怎么看待身边这些人类？’想想看，要是我们找到了一种方法来让机器人回答这些问题，那不是很酷吗？”<ref name="CastFass2">{{cite journal | last=Ditzian | first=Eric | accessdate=2013-12-25 |url=http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2011/09/28/prometheus-damon-lindelof/ | title='Prometheus' Scribe Damon Lindelof Talks Robots, Slimy Corporations & Ridley Scott Collab | publisher=MTV | date=2011-09-28 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130610124112/http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2011/09/28/prometheus-damon-lindelof/ |archivedate=2013-06-10 |deadurl=no}}</ref>法斯賓達表示：“在大卫看来，人类船员有些孩子气。他的嫉妒和傲慢都是因为他意识到自己的知识包罗万象，因此比人类更加优越。大卫希望自己的才能受到认可和称赞。”<ref name="Cast30" />在发展自己角色的过程中，法斯賓達没有去观察和模仿《异形》和《[[异形2|异形2]]》中的机器人角色，而是对斯科特1982年科幻片《[[银翼杀手|银翼杀手]]》中的复制人进行观察，他特别关注其中[[肖恩·杨|肖恩·杨]]（{{lang|en|Sean Young}}）扮演的瑞切尔（{{lang|en|Rachael}}）一角，对其缺少但又渴望拥有灵魂的特点很感兴趣<ref name="CastFass5">{{cite web |url=http://www.slashfilm.com/interview-michael-fassbender-talks-prometheus/ |title=Interview: Michael Fassbender Talks ‘Prometheus’|last=Sciretta | first= Peter |publisher=/Film |date=2012-06-08 |accessdate=2013-12-25 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130618232546/http://www.slashfilm.com/interview-michael-fassbender-talks-prometheus/ | archivedate=2013-06-18 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。此外，《[[2001太空漫遊_(電影)|2001太空漫遊]]》中[[哈儿|哈儿]]计算机的声音<ref name="CastFass5" />，[[奥运会|奥运会]][[跳水|跳水]][[运动员|运动员]][[格雷格·洛加尼斯|格雷格·洛加尼斯]]的动作特点<ref name="Sequel2">{{cite web |first= Dave |last=Trumbore |title=WonderCon 2012: Prometheus Panel Recap Featuring Sir Ridley Scott and Damon Lindelof |url=http://collider.com/prometheus-wondercon/152633/ | publisher=Collider.com |date=2012-03-17 |accessdate=2013-12-25 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131127110411/http://collider.com/prometheus-wondercon/152633/ |archivedate= 2013-11-27 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="CastFass4">{{cite web |url=http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2011/11/17/michael-fassbender-prometheus-greg-louganis/ |title=Michael Fassbender's 'Prometheus' Character Inspired By... Greg Louganis? |last=Sullivan |first=Kevin |publisher=MTV Movies Blog |date=2011-11-17 |accessdate=2013-12-25 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131127120532/http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2011/11/17/michael-fassbender-prometheus-greg-louganis/ |archivedate=2013-11-27 |deadurl=no}}</ref>，还有[[大卫·鲍伊|大卫·鲍伊]]、[[狄·保加第|狄·保加第]]和[[彼得·奧圖|彼得·奧圖]]分别在《[[天外来客_(电影)|天外来客]]》（{{lang|en|''The Man Who Fell to Earth''}}）、《[[仆人_(电影)|仆人]]》（{{lang|en|''The Servant''}}）和《[[阿拉伯的劳伦斯_(电影)|阿拉伯的劳伦斯]]》中的表演都给予了法斯賓達更多的灵感<ref name="Marketing40">{{cite news | last=Robey | first=Tim | url= http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/film-news/9195794/Prometheus-preview.html | title= Prometheus – preview | publisher=Telegraph Media Group | work=The Daily Telegraph | date=2012-04-10 | accessdate=2013-12-25 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131024153124/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/film-news/9195794/Prometheus-preview.html |archivedate= 2013-10-24 |deadurl=no}}</ref>，大卫的金发就是仿照[[托马斯·爱德华·劳伦斯|托马斯·爱德华·劳伦斯]]<ref name="Hewitt" />{{rp|72}}。斯科特很看好由法斯賓達扮演这个角色，之前的报道声称后者的經紀人要求的片酬过高<ref name="paradise found" />，但法斯賓達还是在2011年1月确认出演<ref name="CastFass1">{{cite journal | last1=Kit | first1=Borys | last2=McClintock | first2=Pamela | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/blogs/heat-vision/michael-fassbender-star-opposite-noomi-76403 | title=Michael Fassbender to Star Opposite Noomi Rapace in Ridley Scott's 'Prometheus' | journal=The Hollywood Reporter | date=2011-01-26 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130920212429/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/blogs/heat-vision/michael-fassbender-star-opposite-noomi-76403 |archivedate= 2013-09-20 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。
*[[查理兹·塞隆|查理兹·塞隆]] 饰 梅莉迪丝·维克斯：
:维克斯是韦兰公司的雇员，她的任务是对这次远征进行监控<ref name="Cast30" /><ref name="Hewitt" />{{rp|67}}。塞隆形容这个角色很神秘，其真实身份和目的“随着情节发展而逐渐显露出来”<ref name="CastTheron2">{{cite news | last=Gutierrez | first=Ezequiel | url=http://www.heyuguys.co.uk/20th-century-fox-comic-con-panel-and-footage-description/ | title=20th Century Fox Comic Con Panel and Footage Description | publisher=Hey U Guys | date=2011-07-22 |accessdate=2013-12-25 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130622022236/http://www.heyuguys.co.uk/20th-century-fox-comic-con-panel-and-footage-description/ | archivedate=2013-06-22 |deadurl=no}}</ref>，而且“一定程度上是个反派……（她）肯定事先就有所企图”<ref name="CastTheron3">{{cite news|title=Charlize Theron Explains Her Prometheus Character |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=85455 |date=2011-12-23 |accessdate=2013-12-25 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130919082310/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=85455 | archivedate=2013-09-19 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。她认为“维克斯是个务实的人，极力想要控制住局面”<ref name="Cast30" />。斯科特不希望把这个角色作为电影中的重点，而是让她潜-{}-伏在镜头的背景中观察其他的角色。塞隆称，这有助于让她的角色更有层次感，因为“你一下子就会变得对她充满怀疑”<ref name="Leyland">{{cite journal |last1=Leyland |first1=Matthew |title=Origin of the Species |journal=Total Film |issue=193 |page= |publisher= Future plc|date=2012年6月}}</ref>{{rp|84}}。维克斯和大卫在外貌和举止上的类似之处旨在让观众相信大卫有可能是基于维克斯的{{lang|en|DNA}}，或是维克斯自己就是个机器人<ref name="CastTheron6">{{cite web |url=http://www.slashfilm.com/interview-charlize-theron-talks-prometheus/ |title=Interview: ‘Prometheus’ Star Charlize Theron Talks About Working With Practical Sets vs. CG, Responds to Internet Theories About Her Character and More |last=Sciretta |first= Peter |publisher=/Film |date=2012-06-11 |accessdate=2013-12-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130822041735/http://www.slashfilm.com/interview-charlize-theron-talks-prometheus/ | archivedate=2013-08-22 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。塞隆获选出演这个角色后与斯科特和林道夫合作，给角色增加了三个镜头，来让其形象更加丰满<ref name="THRMay1612">{{cite news |last1=Galloway |first1=Stephen |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/ridley-scott-prometheus-alien-324981?page=2 |title=Return of the 'Alien' Mind (Page 2) |publisher=Prometheus Global Media |work=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2012-05-16 |accessdate=2013-12-25 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68QMQENSn?url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/ridley-scott-prometheus-alien-324981?page=2 |archivedate=2012-06-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。电影中有一些动作场面需要塞隆穿上重达14[[公斤|公斤]]的靴子从沙堆上跑过，这对她来说很困难<ref name="Leyland" />{{rp|84}}。塞隆原本是扮演肖的人选，但由于已经答应出演《[[疯狂的麦克斯：狂暴之路|疯狂的麦克斯：狂暴之路]]》而分身-{}-乏术。之后该片予以推迟，因此塞隆得以重新加入《普罗米修斯》<ref name="Nashawaty-2012">{{cite journal |last1=Nashawaty |first1=Chris |date=2012-05-18 |title=Birth of a New Alien |journal=Entertainment Weekly | publisher= Time Inc. | issue=1207}}</ref>{{rp|7-8}}。[[杨紫琼|杨紫琼]]和[[安吉丽娜·朱莉|安吉丽娜·朱莉]]都曾是这个角色的考虑人选<ref name="Cast1" /><ref name="paradise found" />。
*[[伊德瑞斯·艾尔巴|伊德瑞斯·艾尔巴]] 饰 简尼克：
:简尼克是“普罗米修斯号”的船长<ref name="CastElba1">{{cite web |url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/shadowandact/idris_elba_reveals_bits_pieces_of_prometheus |title=Idris Elba Reveals Bits & Pieces Of "Prometheus" |date=2011-06-09 |publisher=Indie Wire |accessdate=2013-12-25 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68QKsnYH9?url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/shadowandact/idris_elba_reveals_bits_pieces_of_prometheus |archivedate=2012-06-14 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。艾尔巴形容这是一个拥有军事背景的“码头工人和[[水手|水手]]”<ref name="Cast30" /><ref name="Hewitt" />{{rp|66}}。他说：“他的生活就是作为一名船长，船上的船员也是他的责任”<ref name="Cast30" />，而且“他的性格现实而务实。他必须要参与进来……在这样一部充满了理念的电影中，你需要有一个这样的角色，他可以提出像‘等等……为什么我们要这么做？’这样的问题”<ref name="Hewitt" />{{rp|66}}。
*[[盖·皮尔斯|盖·皮尔斯]] 饰 [[彼得·韦兰|彼得·韦兰]]：
:韦兰是韦兰公司的创始-{人}-兼[[首席执行官|CEO]]，拥有亿万身家<ref name="MarketingTED">{{cite web |first=Ben |last=Lillie |title=Writing a TEDTalk from the future: Q&A with Damon Lindelof |url=http://blog.ted.com/2012/02/28/writing-a-tedtalk-from-the-future-q-a-with-damon-lindelof/ |publisher=Sapling Foundation |work=TED |date=2012-02-28 |accessdate=2013-12-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131022140007/http://blog.ted.com/2012/02/28/writing-a-tedtalk-from-the-future-q-a-with-damon-lindelof/ |archivedate=2013-10-22 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="CastPearce4">{{cite news | first=Joseph |last=Gammie | url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/features/alien-the-monster-returns-7717514.html | title=Alien: The monster returns? | date=2012-05-06 | publisher=Independent Print Limited |work=The Independent | accessdate=2013-12-25 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131004224157/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/features/alien-the-monster-returns-7717514.html | archivedate=2013-10-04 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。林道夫形容这个角色非常自负，而且有着严重的[[上帝情结|上帝情结]]（{{lang|en|god complex}}）<ref name="MarketingTED" />。每一次使用假肢和化妆术把皮尔斯改造成年老的韦兰需要5个小时的时间，之后的卸妆又需要一个小时。皮尔斯透过对老年人的动作进行观察来为自己角色的行为作参考，他发现出演这个角色最困难的部分就是不断重复不流畅的身体运动<ref name="CastPearce5">{{cite web|first= Steve |last=Weintraub |title=Guy Pearce Talks Making Prometheus, Viral Marketing, Working for Ridley Scott, and Briefly Mentions Iron Man 3 |url=http://collider.com/guy-pearce-prometheus-iron-man-3-interview/170191/ | publisher=Collider.com |date=2012-05-31 |accessdate=2013-12-25 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20120905120846/http://collider.com/guy-pearce-prometheus-iron-man-3-interview/170191 | archivedate=2012-09-05 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。斯科特原本选择的是[[麥斯·馮·西度|麥斯·馮·西度]]来饰演韦兰，但皮尔斯试镜时让导演觉得既可以由他扮演年长的韦兰，又可以诠释早期剧本草案中的年轻版角色<ref name="io9">{{cite web |url=http://io9.com/5917639/10-things-you-didnt-know-about-the-design-of-prometheus |title=10 Things You Didn’t Know About the Making of Prometheus |author=Anders, Charlie Jane |publisher=''io9'' |date=2012-06-12 |accessdate=2013-12-25 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131007110201/http://io9.com/5917639/10-things-you-didnt-know-about-the-design-of-prometheus |archivedate= 2013-10-07 | deadurl=no}}</ref>。
*[[羅根·馬歇爾-格林|羅根·馬歇爾-格林]] 饰 查理·赫洛维：
:赫洛维是个考古学家，也是肖的情人<ref name="CastGreen2">{{cite news | last=Fleming | first=Mike | url=http://www.deadline.com/2011/03/logan-marshall-green-lands-prometheus/ | title=Logan Marshall-Green Lands 'Prometheus' | publisher=PMC |work=Deadline.com | date=2011-03-14 | accessdate=2013-12-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121011003717/http://www.deadline.com/2011/03/logan-marshall-green-lands-prometheus/ |archivedate=2012-10-11 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="Hewitt" />{{rp|69}}。马歇尔-格林是在出演《[[外外百老匯|外外百老匯]]》后获选在本片中出镜的<ref name="Hewitt" />{{rp|69}}，他形容赫洛维是那种“[[世界极限运动会|极限运动]]型科学家”，并表示自己很喜欢角色身上那种“先跨后看”的哲学理念。他还表示，赫洛维“并不想与自己的创造者见面，他愿意付出很大的代价来达到目的”<ref name="Hewitt" />{{rp|69}}。对于人物的行为动机他说：“他把每件事都做到极致，有时这样更好，但有时也会很糟。我想他这样做都是为了获得探索过程中的那种刺激。”<ref name="Cast30" />马歇尔-格林还把赫洛维与肖进行了这样的对比：“她是位信徒，而我是科学家，是怀疑论者，是无神论者。”<ref name="CastGreen3">{{cite news | last=Gray | first=Richard | url=http://www.thereelbits.com/2012/05/02/exclusive-q-a-with-prometheus-star-logan-marshall-green/ | title=Exclusive: Q & A with Prometheus star Logan Marshall-Green | publisher=The Reel Bits | date=2011-05-02 | accessdate=2013-12-25 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131025094242/http://www.thereelbits.com/2012/05/02/exclusive-q-a-with-prometheus-star-logan-marshall-green/ | archivedate=2013-10-25 |deadurl=no}}</ref>
*[[西恩·哈里斯|西恩·哈里斯]]（{{lang|en|Sean Harris}}） 饰 费菲尔德：
