ef>。2012年4月10日，媒体报道称伦敦莱斯特广场的{{lang|en|Vue}}电影院播放了13分钟的本片开场剪辑片段，并且还是{{lang|en|3D}}格式<ref name="Marketing41">{{cite news|last=Wales |first=George |url=http://www.totalfilm.com/news/prometheus-footage-reveal-report/ |title=Prometheus footage reveal report: details and reaction |publisher=Future plc |work=Total Film |date=2012-04-10 |accessdate=2013-12-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130703133905/http://www.totalfilm.com/news/prometheus-footage-reveal-report/ |archivedate=2013-07-03 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。这些片段，特别是{{lang|en|3D}}视觉效果以及法斯賓達、拉佩斯、塞隆和艾尔巴的表演获得了一致好评<ref name="Marketing40" /><ref name="Marketing41" /><ref name="Marketing42">{{cite news|last=Connell |first=Brendon |url=http://www.bleedingcool.com/2012/04/10/ive-just-seen-bunch-of-scenes-from-prometheus-want-tell-about-them/ |title=I’ve Just Seen A Bunch Of Scenes From Prometheus And Want To Tell You About Them |publisher=Bleeding Cool |date=2012-04-10 |accessdate=2013-12-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131213233351/http://www.bleedingcool.com/2012/04/10/ive-just-seen-bunch-of-scenes-from-prometheus-want-tell-about-them/ |archivedate=2013-12-13 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

2012年4月29日，英国[[第四台_(英国)|第四台]]在[[电视剧|电视剧]]《[[国土安全_(电视剧)|国土安全]]》的第一个广告休息时间里播放了《普罗米修斯》的预告片，这也是该预告片的国际首发。电视台鼓励观众把自己的看法分享到{{lang|en|Twitter}}，其中有一些会在之后的广告休息时间予以广播，这也是历史上首次将观众的推文用到电视广告中<ref name="Marketing50">{{cite news|last=Reynolds |first=Simon |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/news/a378634/prometheus-trailer-watch-the-channel-4-homeland-teaser-ad-video.html |title='Prometheus' trailer: Watch the Channel 4 'Homeland' teaser ad – video |publisher=Hearst Corporation |work=Digital Spy |date=2012-04-29 |accessdate=2013-12-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131101175326/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/news/a378634/prometheus-trailer-watch-the-channel-4-homeland-teaser-ad-video.html |archivedate=2013-11-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="Marketing51">{{cite news|last=Langshaw |first=Mark |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/news/a378623/prometheus-trailer-to-get-live-twitter-response-during-homeland.html |title='Prometheus' trailer to get live Twitter response during 'Homeland' |publisher=Hearst Corporation |work=Digital Spy |date=2012-04-26 |accessdate=2013-12-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131101175131/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/news/a378623/prometheus-trailer-to-get-live-twitter-response-during-homeland.html |archivedate=2013-11-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。[[社交网络服务|社交网络服务]]平台{{lang|en|Zeebox}}还推出了一项有奖竞赛活动，观众有机会赢得影片的电影票<ref name="Marketing52">{{cite news |last=McCabe |first=Maisie |url=http://www.mediaweek.co.uk/article/1129255/ridley-scotts-prometheus-air-first-synchronised-ad-zeebox |title=Ridley Scott's Prometheus to air first synchronised ad on Zeebox |publisher=Prometheus Global Media |work=Mediaweek |date=2012-04-27 |accessdate=2013-12-27 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68TWRPDVX?url=http://m.mediaweek.co.uk/article/1129255/Ridley-Scotts-Prometheus-air-first-synchronised-ad-Zeebox |archivedate=2012-06-16 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。2012年5月8日，英国通訊傳播主管機構{{lang|en|[[Ofcom|Ofcom]]}}开始对这个广告进行涉嫌违反广播条例的调查，据称这是因为广告期间电视荧幕上还存在第四台的[[商标|商标]]时出现了鼓励观众订票的画外音。英国的广播条例要求广告和电视购物必须与其他节目内容有明显区别，因此这个广告有可能触犯了这一规则<ref name="Marketing54">{{cite news |last=Sweney |first=Mark |url=http://www.theguardian.com/media/2012/may/08/channel-4-ofcom-investigation-prometheus-exlusive |title=Channel 4 under Ofcom investigation over Prometheus exclusive |publisher=Guardian Media Group |work=The Guardian |date=2012-05-08 |accessdate=2013-12-27 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68TWUZdb5?url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2012/may/08/channel-4-ofcom-investigation-prometheus-exlusive |archivedate=2012-06-16 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="Marketing55">{{cite news |last=Kemp |first=Stuart |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/ofcom-launches-uk-prometheus-trailer-321538 |title=Ofcom Launches U.K. 'Prometheus' Trailer Probe |publisher=Prometheus Global Media |work=Hollywood Reporter |date=2012-05-08 |accessdate=2013-12-27 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68QLqcZvh?url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/ofcom-launches-uk-prometheus-trailer-321538 |archivedate=2012-06-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

虽然商家通常会避免对促銷偏向成人的电影以接觸到更多的觀眾，但包括[[库尔斯酿酒公司|库尔斯酿酒公司]]、[[亚马逊公司|亚马逊公司]]和{{lang|en|[[Verizon_FiOS|Verizon FiOS]]}}在内的多个商家还是与本片结成了促销合作伙伴关系，估计在营销支持上的花费达到3000万美元。亚马逊会指导感兴趣的用户透过{{lang|en|Fandango}}购买电影票，发给客户的产品中也会附有宣传资料，这是亚马逊首次允许外部公司进行这样的营销<ref name="Marketing71">{{cite news |last=Graser |first=Marc |url=http://variety.com/2012/film/news/coors-amazon-verizon-ride-with-prometheus-1118054160/ |title=Coors, Amazon, Verizon ride with 'Prometheus' |publisher=PMC |work=Variety |date=2012-05-17 |accessdate=2013-12-28 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68TGnG9Ri?url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118054160?refCatId=1 |archivedate=2012-06-16 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。电影在伦敦的首映式透过流媒体在影片的网站和{{lang|en|Verizon FiOS}}的{{lang|en|Facebook}}页面进行直播。{{lang|en|BumeBox}}还对活动进行了促进，从社交网站上收集观众提出的问题，再转交现场的记者进行提问<ref name="Premiere">{{cite news|last1=Warren |first1=Christina |url=http://mashable.com/2012/05/15/prometheus-social-media/ |title=‘Prometheus’ Social Campaign Expands with Live Red Carpet and More |publisher=Mashable Inc. |work=Mashable |date=2012-05-16 |accessdate=2013-12-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131126190544/http://mashable.com/2012/05/15/prometheus-social-media/ |archivedate=2013-11-26 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。[[国家娱乐收藏品协会|国家娱乐收藏品协会]]开发了一系列的《普罗米修斯》动作玩偶，计划在2012年9月发行<ref name="MarketingToy1">{{cite web|title=Prometheus Has Landed! |url=http://necaonline.com/34497/blog/press-releases/prometheus-has-landed/ |publisher=National Entertainment Collectibles Association |date=2012-06-08 |accessdate=2013-12-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130723075220/http://necaonline.com/34497/blog/press-releases/prometheus-has-landed/ |archivedate=2013-07-23 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。一本包含影片制作技术介绍和幕后照片，名为《普罗米修斯：电影的艺术》（{{lang|en|''Prometheus: The Art of the Film''}}）的书于2012年6月12日发行<ref name="MarketingBook1">{{cite web |url=http://www.amazon.com/Prometheus-The-Art-Film-Tie/dp/1781161097/ |title=Prometheus: The Art of the Film (Film Tie in) (Hardcover) |publisher=Amazon.com |accessdate=2013-12-28 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20120402062017/http://www.amazon.com/Prometheus-The-Art-Film-Tie/dp/1781161097 |archivedate=2012-04-02 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

=== 病毒宣传活动 ===
[[File:Prometheus_Viral_3_-_David.jpg|thumb]]之间的市场营销伙伴关系。]]
2012年2月28日，《普罗米修斯》以一段影片开始病毒式行销活动，由皮尔斯扮演的彼得・韦兰在影片中发表了一段演说，阐述了自己对未来的设想。影片的时代背景为2023年，呈现了未来[[TED大会|TED大会]]的远景，这是一场一年一度在加利福尼亚州[[长滩_(加利福尼亚州)|长滩]]举行的技术和设计活动。这个片段由斯科特和林道夫构想和设计，斯科特的儿子卢克（{{lang|en|Luke}}）执导。作品与{{lang|en|TED}}合作并以其为背景是因为林道夫希望让更多的人了解这一活动。林道夫表示，镜头中的事情发生在一个未来的体育馆是因为：「像彼得·韦兰这样一个非常自负的人十有八九会对{{lang|en|TED}}说：『要是你想让我发表一场演说，我只会在[[温布利球场|温布利球场]]进行。』」<ref name="MarketingTED" />

{{lang|en|TED}}社区主任汤姆・里利（{{lang|en|Tom Rielly}}）帮助电影制作人获得了使用{{lang|en|TED}}品牌的许可，这也是该品牌首度用于促销目的。里利参与了对影片中2023年大会的设计，并表示这次合作给{{lang|en|TED}}的网站带去了数百万的独立访问次数<ref name="Marketing31">{{cite news |first=Julian |last=Sancton | url=http://www.businessweek.com/articles/2012-03-22/ted-goes-to-the-movies-with-prometheus-promotion | title=TED Goes to the Movies With 'Prometheus' Promotion |publisher= Bloomberg L.P. |work=Bloomberg Businessweek |date=2012-03-22 |accessdate=2013-12-27 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131204231904/http://www.businessweek.com/articles/2012-03-22/ted-goes-to-the-movies-with-prometheus-promotion |archivedate=2013-12-04 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。影片发布的同时，网站上还出现了有关2023年大会的虚构[[博客|博客]]，还有一个虚构的韦兰公司网站<ref name="CastPearce1">{{cite web |first= Matt |last=Goldberg |title=Watch Prometheus’ Peter Weyland (Guy Pearce) Give a TED Talk from 2023 |url=http://collider.com/prometheus-ted-talk-guy-pearce-peter-weyland/148681/ | publisher=Collider.com |date=2012-02-28 |accessdate=2013-12-27 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20120817103408/http://collider.com/prometheus-ted-talk-guy-pearce-peter-weyland/148681 | archivedate=2012-08-17 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="Marketing21">{{cite journal |first=Chris |last=Shea | title=A TED Talk, Circa 2023 |url=http://blogs.wsj.com/ideas-market/2012/03/01/a-ted-talk-circa-2023/ |journal=The Wall Street Journal – Ideas Market blog |date=2012-03-01 |accessdate=2013-12-27 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130612053204/http://blogs.wsj.com/ideas-market/2012/03/01/a-ted-talk-circa-2023/ |archivedate=2013-06-12 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。2012年3月6日，韦兰公司的网站进行了更新，访客可以参与一个向公司投资的游戏，进而发现新的《普罗米修斯》媒体<ref name="MarketingArg1">{{cite news|first=Eric |last=Eisenberg |title=Prometheus Viral Reveals Stunning New Image |url=http://www.cinemablend.com/new/Prometheus-Viral-Reveals-Stunning-Image-29828.html |publisher=Cinema Blend |date=2013-03-06 |accessdate=2013-12-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131225130922/http://www.cinemablend.com/new/Prometheus-Viral-Reveals-Stunning-Image-29828.html |archivedate=2013-12-25 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

2012年{{lang|en|WonderCon}}展会期间，来到本片展台前的参与者将获得一张韦兰公司的名片，上面印有网址和电话号码，用户拨通该号码后会收到一条来自韦兰公司的信息，其中包括有一段影片的链接，这段影片是韦兰公司「大卫8号」机器人的广告，由法斯賓達解说<ref name="MarketingViral2">{{cite web |first= Adam |last=Chitwood |title=Prometheus Viral Campaign Continues with Android-Unboxing Video from Weyland Corp Featuring Michael Fassbender |url=http://collider.com/prometheus-viral-video/153007/ | publisher=Collider.com |date=2012-03-17 |accessdate=2013-12-28 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131111110025/http://collider.com/prometheus-viral-video/153007/ |archivedate=2013-11-11 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。2012年4月17日又发布了这段影片的扩展版本，其中列举了这种机器人的特点，包括无缝复制人类情绪并且不受道德约束和困扰的能力<ref name="MarketingViral3">{{cite web|first= Matt |last=Goldberg |title=Excellent Prometheus Viral Campaign Continues with an Ad for Michael Fassbender’s Android, "David" |url=http://collider.com/prometheus-viral-video-michael-fassbender/159761/ | publisher=Collider.com |date=2012-04-17 |accessdate=2013-12-28 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20120818234942/http://collider.com/prometheus-viral-video-michael-fassbender/159761 |archivedate=2012-08-18 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="MarketingViral4">{{cite news |last1=Zakarin |first1=Jordan |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/prometheus-ad-david-michael-fassbender-ridley-scott-312889 |accessdate=2013-12-28 |title='Prometheus' Ad Touts Michael Fassbender as Weyland Industries Robot David (Video) |publisher=Prometheus Global Media |work=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2012-04-17 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68QLu2YJD?url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/prometheus-ad-david-michael-fassbender-ridley-scott-312889 |archivedate=2012-06-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。《[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]》刊登了一整页的“大卫8号”广告，并且还有开通{{lang|en|Twitter}}账号，以便{{lang|en|Twitter}}用户向其提出问题<ref name="MarketingViral16">{{cite news|last1=Warren |first1=Christina |url=http://mashable.com/2012/04/17/prometheus-david-ad/ |title=‘Prometheus’ Ad Shows Us the Robot We All Want (EXCLUSIVE) |publisher=Mashable Inc. |work=Mashable |date=2012-04-17 |accessdate=2013-12-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131214003235/http://mashable.com/2012/04/17/prometheus-david-ad/ |archivedate=2013-12-14 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。{{lang|en|Verizon FiOS}}提供了对“普罗米修斯号”太空船的虚拟旅程<ref name="MarketingViral16" />。2012年5月16日，一段名为“宁静之眼”（{{lang|en|Quiet Eye}}）的影片在{{lang|en|Verizon FIOS}}的{{lang|en|Facebook}}页面上首次亮相，其中有拉佩斯扮演的肖一角<ref name="Premiere" />透过电话呼叫韦兰公司请求援助寻找外星生命，但这段通话被《异形》系列电影中的{{lang|en|Yutani}}公司监听了<ref name="MarketingViral17">{{cite news|last=Plumb |first=Ali |url=http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=33977 |title=Rapace Stars In New Prometheus Viral |publisher=Bauer Media Group |work=Empire |date=2012-05-16 |accessdate=2013-12-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130620015000/http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=33977 |archivedate=2013-06-20 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。法国[[巴黎地铁|巴黎地铁]]的圣马丁（{{lang|en|Saint-Martin}}）[[巴黎地铁幽灵车站|幽灵车站]]经装修转变成与本片中的外星建筑类似，路过的地铁乘客都可以看到<ref name="Marketing73">{{cite news |first=Cyriaque |last=Lamar |title=An abandoned French subway station was turned into the set of Prometheus |url=http://io9.com/5911447/an-abandoned-french-subway-station-was-turned-into-the-set-of-prometheus | publisher=Gawker Media |work=io9 |date=2011-07-12 |accessdate=2013-12-28 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130618054518/http://io9.com/5911447/an-abandoned-french-subway-station-was-turned-into-the-set-of-prometheus |archivedate=2013-06-18 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。电影上映后，病毒宣传活动仍在继续，一个新的网站上列出了影片片尾的字幕，还包含有一段彼得・韦兰的影片，他在其中引用了[[弗里德里希·尼采|弗里德里希·尼采]]的哲学小说《[[查拉图斯特拉如是说|查拉图斯特拉如是说]]》<ref name="MarketingViral20">{{cite web |first= Matt |last=Goldberg |title=Prometheus Viral Campaign Continues with New Video and Website |url=http://collider.com/prometheus-viral-what-is-10-11-12/172328/ | publisher=Collider.com |date=2012-06-11 |accessdate=2013-12-28 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130723180517/http://collider.com/prometheus-viral-what-is-10-11-12/172328/ |archivedate=2013-07-23 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="MarketingViral21">{{cite web|last=Vary |first=Adam |title='Prometheus' end credits reveal yet another viral video, and allusions to Nietzsche -- Video |url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2012/06/11/prometheus-nietzsche-zarathustra/ |work=Inside Movies blog |publisher=Entertainment Weekly |accessdate=2013-12-28 |date=2012-06-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131015020626/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2012/06/11/prometheus-nietzsche-zarathustra/ |archivedate=2013-10-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。另一段影片于2012年9月发布，其中有艾尔巴扮演的船长简尼克准备出发执行任务<ref name="MarketingViralSep">{{cite web |first= Adam |last=Chitwood |title=Prometheus Viral Continues? Mysterious New Clip Featuring Idris Elba Surfaces |url=http://collider.com/prometheus-video-idris-elba/193924/ | publisher=Collider.com |date=2012-09-07 |accessdate=2013-12-28 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20121108143132/http://collider.com/prometheus-video-idris-elba/193924/ |archivedate=2012-11-08 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

在2012年5月的數位好莱坞（{{lang|en|Digital Hollywood}}）大会上，林道夫表示这些影片源于影片作为《异形》前传的地位问题，他们相信制作由片中明星出演的影片会比任何有关本片和《异形》系列电影联系的评论更有吸引力。他还表示，这些影片应该要够酷，让观众感到物有所值，同时又不能太过关键，以免在最终上映的电影中没有这些内容时对观众的感观产生不利影响。<ref name="MarketingViral18">{{cite news |last=Krinsky |first=Tamara |url=http://www.tubefilter.com/2012/05/08/lost-creator-damon-lindelof-prometheus-viral-videos-twitter/ |title=‘Lost’ Co-Creator Talks ‘Prometheus’ Viral Videos, Twitter |publisher=Tubefilter |date=2012-05-08 |accessdate=2013-12-28 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68TWtK5e6?url=http://www.tubefilter.com/2012/05/08/lost-creator-damon-lindelof-prometheus-viral-videos-twitter/ |archivedate=2012-06-16 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

