《普罗米修斯》于2012年5月31日在伦敦莱斯特广场的[[帝国电影院|帝国电影院]]举行了首映式<ref name="Release6">{{cite news | last=Szalai| first=George | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/prometheus-charlize-theron-michael-fassbender-ridley-scott-331878 | title=Charlize Theron, Michael Fassbender Attend London Premiere of Ridley Scott’s 'Prometheus' | publisher=Prometheus Global Media |work=The Hollywood Reporter | date=2012-05-31 |accessdate=2013-12-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120619043831/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/prometheus-charlize-theron-michael-fassbender-ridley-scott-331878 |archivedate=2012-06-19 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="Premiere2">{{cite news | last1=Flynn | first1=Richard | url=http://www.screendaily.com/news/uk-ireland/londons-leicester-square-re-opens-after-18-month-renovation/5042642.article | title=London's Leicester Square re-opens after 18 month renovation |publisher=Screen International | date=2012-05-24 | accessdate=2013-12-26 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130619200850/http://www.screendaily.com/news/uk-ireland/londons-leicester-square-re-opens-after-18-month-renovation/5042642.article |archivedate=2013-06-19 |deadurl=no}}</ref>，再于次日起在英国发行<ref name="Rating1">{{cite news|last=Langshaw |first=Mark |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/news/a380747/prometheus-gets-15-certificate-in-uk-passed-uncut.html |title='Prometheus' gets 15 certificate in UK, passed uncut |publisher=Hearst Corporation |work=Digital Spy |date=2012-05-09 |accessdate=2013-12-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131101175725/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/news/a380747/prometheus-gets-15-certificate-in-uk-passed-uncut.html |archivedate=2013-11-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，6月8日起在北美上映<ref name="Release1" />。电影的{{lang|en|[[IMAX|IMAX]]}}和{{lang|en|3D}}版本也同时上映<ref name="Release2">{{cite web|url=http://www.deadline.com/2012/03/ridley-scotts-prometheus-to-get-imax-3d-release-june-8/ |title='Prometheus' To Get IMAX 3D Release |date=2012-03-08 |publisher=PMC |work=Deadline.com |accessdate=2013-12-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120623011309/http://www.deadline.com/2012/03/ridley-scotts-prometheus-to-get-imax-3d-release-june-8 |archivedate=2012-06-23 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，还进行了{{lang|en|D-Box}}运动座椅编码来向电影观众提供物理性的反馈<ref name="ReleaseDBox">{{cite news|url=http://www.3dfocus.co.uk/3d-news-2/prometheus-to-be-d-box-encoded-cineworld-interview/8430 |title=Prometheus to be D-BOX encoded – Cineworld interview |publisher=3D Focus |date=2012-05-09 |accessdate=2013-12-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131105090036/http://www.3dfocus.co.uk/3d-news-2/prometheus-to-be-d-box-encoded-cineworld-interview/8430 |archivedate=2013-11-05 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

=== 预发行 ===
电影在英国上映前预售出的电影票价值约有100万[[英镑|英镑]]<ref name="BOInternational1">{{cite news | last=Finke | first=Nikki | url=http://www.deadline.com/2012/05/prometheus-begins-foreign-run-1-france/ | title=Ridley Scott Directing ‘Prometheus’ Begins Foreign Run: #1 France | publisher=PMC |work=Deadline.com | date=2012-05-30 | accessdate=2013-12-26 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120804055614/http://www.deadline.com/2012/05/prometheus-begins-foreign-run-1-france/ |archivedate=2012-08-04 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。英国最大的{{lang|en|IMAX}}电影院{{lang|en|[[伦敦IMAX|伦敦IMAX]]}}预售出18827张电影票，以29万3312英镑的成绩刷新了该影院预发行最高周票房纪录，也以13万7000英镑刷新了单日预售的票房纪录<ref name="Release3">{{cite news |last=Stuart |first=Kemp |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/ridley-scott-prometheus-breaks-IMAX-record-320348 |title=Ridley Scott’s 'Prometheus' Breaks IMAX U.K. Pre-Sales Record |publisher=Prometheus Global Media |work=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2012-05-04 |accessdate=2013-12-26 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68QM1kUvj?url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/ridley-scott-prometheus-breaks-IMAX-record-320348 |archivedate=2012-06-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。最终《普罗米修斯》在这家电影院一共预售出30000张票，进账47万零977英镑，超越《[[哈利·波特与死亡圣器（下）|哈利·波特与死亡圣器（下）]]》和《阿凡达》成为该影院预订量最高的电影<ref name="Release4">{{cite news |last=Stuart |first=Kemp |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/ridley-scott-prometheus-BFI-Imax-record-330052 |title='Prometheus' Continues to Build Imax U.K. Pre-Sales Record |publisher=Prometheus Global Media |work=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2012-05-28 |accessdate=2013-12-26 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68QM5GZ4j?url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/ridley-scott-prometheus-BFI-Imax-record-330052 |archivedate=2012-06-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

对北美电影观众进行的追踪调查结果显示，男性观众对本片非常感兴趣，而女性观众则相反<ref name="ReleaseUSPre">{{cite news |last=McClintock |first=Pamela |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-preview-madagascar-3-prometheus-334895 |title=Box Office Preview: 'Madagascar 3' Likely to Beat 'Prometheus' For No. 1 in U.S. |publisher=Prometheus Global Media |work=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2012-06-07 |accessdate=2013-12-26 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68QMB5R63?url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-preview-madagascar-3-prometheus-334895 |archivedate=2012-06-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。影片在北美的上映时间与《[[荒失失奇兵3：歐洲逐隻捉|荒失失奇兵3：歐洲逐隻捉]]》相同，后者是2012年暑期美国电影市场上的第一部老少皆宜的作品，媒体在哪一部电影能在上映首周拔得头筹问题上的预测相互矛盾<ref name="chicago1">{{cite news |title=Box Office Preview: 'Prometheus' vs. 'Madagascar 3' Is Too Close to Call |url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/sns-rt-box-office-madagascar-3mt1thewrap43126-20120607,0,5367750.story |publisher=Chicago Tribune |first=Todd |last=Todd Cunningham |date=2012-06-07 |accessdate=2012-06-08 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68GORcVTD?url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/sns-rt-box-office-madagascar-3mt1thewrap43126-20120607,0,5367750.story |archivedate=2012-06-08 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。2012年6月6日，一份调查显示有42%的日报认为《普罗米修斯》将会打败《荒失失奇兵3：歐洲逐隻捉》。而互联网上的追踪显示，《普罗米修斯》的关注度每多发布一个宣传片后就会出现飙升<ref name="boxofficecom1">{{cite news |title=Weekend Predictions: 'Prometheus' and 'Madagascar 3: Europe's Most Wanted' |url=http://www.boxoffice.com/featured_stories/2012-06-weekend-predictions-prometheus-and-madagascar-3-europes-most-wanted |publisher=boxoffice.com |first=Phil |last=Contrino |date=2012-06-06 |accessdate=2013-12-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120610041948/http://www.boxoffice.com/featured_stories/2012-06-weekend-predictions-prometheus-and-madagascar-3-europes-most-wanted |archivedate=2012-06-10 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。媒体预计《普罗米修斯》上映首周收入为3000万美元，而《荒失失奇兵3：歐洲逐隻捉》则有4500万美元左右<ref name="THR-predict">{{cite news |title=Box Office Preview: 'Madagascar 3' Likely to Beat 'Prometheus' For No. 1 in U.S. |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-preview-madagascar-3-prometheus-334895 |publisher=The Hollywood Reporter |first=Pamela |last=McClintock |date=2012-06-07 |accessdate=2013-12-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120613210704/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-preview-madagascar-3-prometheus-334895 |archivedate=2012-06-13 |deadurl=no}}</ref>，随着周末的临近，追踪调查显示《荒失失奇兵3：歐洲逐隻捉》首周收入约为5500万美元，《普罗米修斯》则为5000至5500万美元<ref name="latimes-predict">{{cite news|title=Movie Projector: 'Madagascar 3' could edge out 'Prometheus' |url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/cotown/la-et-ct-box-office-madagascar-prometheus--20120607,0,1399649.story |publisher=Los Angeles Times |first=Amy |last=Kaufman |date=2012-06-07 |accessdate=2013-12-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131008114419/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/cotown/la-et-ct-box-office-madagascar-prometheus--20120607%2C0%2C1399649.story |archivedate=2013-10-08 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。由于分级上比《荒失失奇兵3：歐洲逐隻捉》更严，放映《普罗米修斯》 的[[电影院|电影院]]数量要少264家<ref name="BOM-forecast">{{cite news |title=Forecast: 'Prometheus,' 'Madagascar 3' Go Head-to-Head This Weekend |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3459&p=.htm |publisher=Amazon.com | work=Box Office Mojo |first=Ray |last=Subers |date=2012-06-07 |accessdate=2013-12-26 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130510145334/http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3459&p=.htm |archivedate= 2013-05-10 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
《普罗米修斯》整体获得了商业上的成功。影片在北美获得了开门红，虽然尚未达到电影公司的预期，但在其他国家上映期间一直有强势表现<ref name="BOSuccess">{{cite web |first=Paul |last=Shirey | url=http://www.joblo.com/movie-news/cmon-hollywood-dont-give-up-on-prometheus-2 | title=C'mon Hollywood: Don't Give Up On The Prometheus Sequel! | publisher=JoBlo.com | date=2013-04-16 | accessdate=2013-12-26 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130923204819/http://www.joblo.com/movie-news/cmon-hollywood-dont-give-up-on-prometheus-2 |archivedate=2013-09-23 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="BOSuccess2">{{cite web |first=Ben |last=Arnold | url=http://uk.movies.yahoo.com/prometheus-writer-won-t-be-penning-sequel-120009893.html | title=Prometheus writer won't be penning sequel | publisher=[[Yahoo!|Yahoo!]] | date=2012-12-21 | accessdate=2013-12-26 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130523065321/http://uk.movies.yahoo.com/prometheus-writer-won-t-be-penning-sequel-120009893.html |archivedate=2013-05-23 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="BOSuccess3">{{cite news |first=Charlie Jane |last=Anders |title=Is the Prometheus sequel stalled out just because nobody knows how to follow that ending? |url=http://io9.com/is-the-prometheus-sequel-stalled-out-just-because-nobod-461244398 | publisher=Gawker Media |work=io9 |date=2013-03-27 |accessdate=2013-12-26 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131007091225/http://io9.com/is-the-prometheus-sequel-stalled-out-just-because-nobod-461244398 |archivedate=2013-10-07 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="BOSuccess4">{{cite web|first=Ray |last=Subers | url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3479&p=.htm |title=Five $50 Million Debuts Propel June Business | publisher=Amazon.com |work=Box Office Mojo |date=2012-07-06 |accessdate=2013-12-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131110051547/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3479&p=.htm |archivedate=2013-11-10 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="BOSuccess5">{{cite web |first=Ray |last=Subers |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3527&p=.htm |title=Around-the-World Roundup: 'Resident Evil' Slays With $49.6 Million Debut |publisher=Amazon.com |work=Box Office Mojo |date=2012-09-18 |accessdate=2013-12-26 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6GoeIqgTo?url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3527 |archivedate=2013-05-22 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。影片在北美进账1亿2647万7084美元，其他国家2亿7687万7385美元，全球总票房为4亿零335万4469美元<ref name="BOM" />，在2012年的所有电影中可以排到第18位<ref name="BOM2012">{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?view2=worldwide&yr=2012&p=.htm |title=2012 Worldwide Grosses | publisher=Amazon.com |work=Box Office Mojo |year=2012 |accessdate=2013-12-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131211080611/http://boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?view2=worldwide&yr=2012&p=.htm |archivedate= 2013-12-11 |deadurl=no}}</ref>，如果不考虑[[通货膨胀|通货膨胀]]因素，截止2013年12月中旬，这个成绩也可以在世界电影历史票房总榜上名列第178位<ref name="BOM" />。

从2012年5月30日至6月1日——北美市场发行前一星期——《普罗米修斯》先后在15个[[国家|国家]]和[[地区|地区]]上映。之所以提前上映是为了避免与下星期开始的[[2012年欧洲足球锦标赛|2012年欧洲足球锦标赛]]竞争。电影在英国上映的第一天收入为339万美元<ref name="BOInternational2">{{cite news | last=Finke | first=Nikki | url=http://www.deadline.com/2012/06/snow-white-and-the-huntsman-opens-to-1-383m-midnights-from-1092-theaters-better-than-mib3/ | title=‘Snow White’ $56.1M Domestic Breaks Box Office Slump: $95.4M Global; ‘Prometheus’ On Fire In UK Ahead Of Domestic Opening; ‘Marvel’s The Avengers #3 Film Of All Time | publisher=PMC |work=Deadline.com | date=2012-06-02 | accessdate=2013-12-26 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20120904051053/http://www.deadline.com/2012/06/snow-white-and-the-huntsman-opens-to-1-383m-midnights-from-1092-theaters-better-than-mib3/ |archivedate=2012-09-04 |deadurl=no}}</ref>，[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]为220万美元<ref name="BoInternational3">{{cite news | last=McClintock | first=Pamela | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-prometheus-snow-white-uk-332235 | title=Box Office Report: 'Prometheus' Opening Ahead of 'Snow White' in the U.K. | publisher=Prometheus Global Media | work=The Hollywood Reporter | date=2012-06-01 | accessdate=2013-12-26 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20120818133249/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-prometheus-snow-white-uk-332235 |archivedate=2012-08-18 |deadurl=no}}</ref>，[[法国|法国]]为150万美元<ref name="BOInternational1" />。影片在这15个市场上的4695家电影院首周共计进账3480万美元，登上了其中14个市场的周票房冠军宝座，平均每家电影院收入7461美元。不过总体票房成绩则落后于《[[黑衣人3|黑衣人3]]》和《[[白雪公主与猎人|白雪公主与猎人]]》屈居第三位<ref name="BOInterOpeningWeekend">{{cite news |last=Segers |first=Frank |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/foreign-box-office-men-black-mib3-snow-white-huntsman-ridley-scott-prometheus-332448 |title=Foreign Box Office: 'Men in Black 3' Stays No. 1 Overseas With $275 Million-Plus |publisher=Prometheus Global Media |work=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2012-06-03 |accessdate=2013-12-26 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68N0lzAkc?url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/foreign-box-office-men-black-mib3-snow-white-huntsman-ridley-scott-prometheus-332448 |archivedate=2012-06-12 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。电影在英国、[[爱尔兰|爱尔兰]]和[[马耳他|马耳他]]上映首周进账1010万美元，俄罗斯和[[独联体|独联体]]国家为980万美元，法国和[[马格里布|马格里布]]地区为668万美元<ref name="BOM-overseas">{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&id=prometheus.htm |title=Prometheus (2012) - International Box Office Results |publisher=Amazon.com |work=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2013-12-26 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130515145318/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&id=prometheus.htm |archivedate= 2013-05-15 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="BOInterOpeningWeekend2">{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3457&p=.htm |title=Around-the-World Roundup: 'MIB 3' Leads Again, 'Prometheus' Opens Strong | publisher=Amazon.com |work=Box Office Mojo |date=2012-06-05 |accessdate=2013-12-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131030140359/http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3457&p=.htm |archivedate=2013-10-30 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。到了6月8日，影片已经在共计50个市场上发行，并且在[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]和[[韩国|韩国]]的上映首周都获得了成功，分别收入720万和420万美元<ref name="overseas-second">{{cite news|url=http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3462&p=.htm |title=Around-the-World: 'Madagascar 3' Skips Europe, Wins Overseas Anyway |first=Ray |last=Subers |date=2012-06-10 |publisher=Amazon.com |work=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2013-12-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029191258/http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3462&p=.htm |archivedate=2013-10-29 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。本片于8月下旬在日本上映，收入960万美元<ref name="BOIntJAP">{{cite web |first=Ray |last=Subers | url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3508&p=.htm |title=Around-the-World Roundup: 'Expendables 2' Flexes Muscles Overseas | publisher=Amazon.com |work=Box Office Mojo |date=2012-08-28 |accessdate=2013-12-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131023172648/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3508&p=.htm |archivedate=2013-10-23 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

《普罗米修斯》在北美上映首日就获得了2140万美元的票房收入，之前一晚在1368家电影院放映午夜场又收入了356万1000美元，其中294家{{lang|en|IMAX}}电影院进账103万美元<ref name="BONA1">{{cite news | last=Finke | first=Nikki | url=http://www.deadline.com/2012/06/prometheus-box-office-weekend-fox/ | title=HOT WEEKEND! Both ‘Madagascar 3′ And ‘Prometheus’ On Fire For $59.6M/$49.5M | publisher=PMC |work=Deadline.com | date=2012-06-10 | accessdate=2013-12-26 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130723125058/http://www.deadline.com/2012/06/prometheus-box-office-weekend-fox/ |archivedate= 2013-07-23 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。影片首周在3396家电影院共计收入5105万美元，平均每家15032美元，在票房榜上名列第二位，仅次于收入6040万美元的《荒失失奇兵3：歐洲逐隻捉》，这也是斯科特执导电影上映首周的第二好成绩，落后于2001年的惊悚片《[[人魔|人魔]]》。在所有首周登上票房榜[[亚军|亚军]]位置的电影中，本片可以排到第三位，还可以在所有前传电影中排到第九位，所有[[美国电影分级制度|R级]]电影中排第十位。电影上映首周的观众中男性占57%，25岁以上观众占64%，两项都创下了新的纪录。影片的票房收入中有54%属于{{lang|en|3D}}放映收入，其中{{lang|en|IMAX}}占18%<ref name="BOM" /><ref name="BOM-opening">{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3461&p=.htm |title=Weekend Report: 'Madagascar' Breaks Out, 'Prometheus' Catches Fire|publisher=Amazon.com|work=Box Office Mojo|first=Ray |last=Subers |date=2012-06-10 |accessdate=2013-12-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131030130548/http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3461&p=.htm |archivedate= 2013-10-30 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="BONA2">{{cite news | last=McClintock | first=Pamela | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-report-madagascar-3-prometheus-ridley-scott-snow-white-mib3-335587 | title=Box Office Report: 'Madagascar 3' No. 1 With $60.4 Mil, 'Prometheus' Strong No. 2 With $50 Mil | publisher=Prometheus Global Media | work=The Hollywood Reporter | date=2012-06-10 | accessdate=2013-12-26 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130724111648/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-report-madagascar-3-prometheus-ridley-scott-snow-white-mib3-335587 |archivedate= 2013-07-24 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。影片于2012年9月20日结束放映，共计上映105天，票房收益1亿2647万7084美元。截止2013年12月中旬，本片在所有上映期间从未登上票房榜冠军宝座的电影中票房可以排到第52位<ref name="BOM" />。

=== 专业评价 ===
[[File:Michael_Fassbender_by_Gage_Skidmore.jpg|thumb]]
《普罗米修斯》上映后获得的评价总价趋于正面。根据[[烂蕃茄|烂蕃茄]]上收集的269篇评论文章，其中有198篇给出了“新鲜”的正面评价，“新鲜度”为74%，[[加权平均数|平均得分]]6.9（最高10分），该网站上对本片的共识评价中写道：“雷德利·斯科特这部野心勃勃的《异形》準前传并不能回答所有的重大问题，但仍然让观众享受到了令人难忘的壮观视觉场面和令人信服的表演——特别是麥克·法斯賓達诠释的考究机器人。”<ref name="RottenTomatoes">{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/prometheus_2012/ |title=Prometheus (2012) |publisher = Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2013-12-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131211022519/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/prometheus_2012/ |archivedate=2013-12-11 |deadurl=no}}</ref>而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上收集的42篇评论文章中，有24篇给出好评，1篇差评，17篇褒贬不一，这也属于总体正面的评价<ref name="Metacritic">{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/prometheus |title=Prometheus |publisher=Metacritic |accessdate=2013-12-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110609003633/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/prometheus |archivedate=2011-06-09 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]}}进行的[[市场调查|市场调查]]显示影迷对本片的平均评价为“{{lang|en|B}}”（最好{{lang|en|A+}}，最差{{lang|en|F}}），其中25岁以下观众对其评价最高，为{{lang|en|A-}}<ref name="BONA1" /><ref name="BONA3">{{cite news |first=Andrew |last=Stewart |url=http://variety.com/2012/film/news/madagascar-prometheus-triumph-at-b-o-1118055302/ |title='Madagascar,' 'Prometheus' triumph at B.O. |publisher=PMC |work=Variety |date=2012-06-10 |accessdate=2013-12-27 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68QKc32Uh?url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118055302?refCatId=13 |archivedate=2012-06-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。多份评价中称赞了整部电影的视觉美感和设计，法斯賓達扮演的机器人大卫更是获得了几乎一致性的好评。不过对于本片的剧情，影评人褒贬不一，他们批评剧情缺乏惊喜或是留下了没有解决的问题，对片中的动作和恐怖戏码也产生了不利影响<ref name="RottenTomatoes" /><ref name="RevSum1">{{cite news |first=Oliver |last=Gettell |url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/movies/2012/06/prometheus-ridley-scott-movie-reviews-critics.html |title='Prometheus' comes up short of 'Alien' aspirations, critics say |date=2012-06-08 |accessdate=2013-12-28 |work=Los Angeles Times |publisher=Tribune Company | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20120621180807/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/movies/2012/06/prometheus-ridley-scott-movie-reviews-critics.html |archivedate=2012-06-21 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="RevSum2">{{cite news |first=Luke |last=Holland |url=http://www.nme.com/blogs/the-movies-blog/prometheus-those-mysteries-and-plot-holes-explained |title='Prometheus' - Those Mysteries And Plot Holes Explained |date=2012-06-13 |accessdate=2013-12-28 |work=NME |publisher=Time Inc. |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6GrdCgzFJ?url=http://www.nme.com/blogs/the-movies-blog/prometheus-those-mysteries-and-plot-holes-explained |archivedate=2013-05-24 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="RevSum3">{{cite news |first=David |last=Howland |url=http://whatculture.com/film/prometheus-the-gift-and-the-curse-of-alien.php |title=Prometheus: The Gift and the Curse of Alien |date=2012-07-01 |accessdate=2013-12-27 |work=WhatCulture! |publisher=Obsessed With Film LTD |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6GreKa0Ok?url=http://whatculture.com/film/prometheus-the-gift-and-the-curse-of-alien.php |archivedate=2013-05-24 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

《[[好莱坞报道|好莱坞报道]]》的托德·麦卡锡（{{lang|en|Todd McCarthy}}）称赞影片的视觉效果生动、惊人，在技术层面上达到了壮观的水平，还表扬了法斯賓達、拉佩斯和塞隆的表演，不过他也认为电影一方面冒险前往意外目的地的设定虽然让人感到兴奋，但另一方面也有些过于迎合观众的期望<ref name="RevTHR">{{cite news |title=Prometheus: Film Review |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movie/prometheus/review/330414 |first=Todd |last=McCarthy |work=The Hollywood Reporter |publisher=Prometheus Global Media |date=2012-05-30 |accessdate=2013-12-28 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131030111440/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movie/prometheus/review/330414 |archivedate=2013-10-30 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。《[[Time_Out|Time Out伦敦]]》的汤姆·赫德尔斯顿（{{lang|en|Tom Huddleston}}）对影片的摄影和设计有高度评价，但是“剧本感觉很平淡……对白存在偷懒，而剧情虽然堆满了引人注目的概念，但就是没法凝聚起来。在令人愉悦的设定背后，其核心表现很鬆垮和混乱，有些时候还略显沉闷，高潮戏空有精彩的镜头，但没有真正的气势。”<ref name="RevTimeOutLon">{{cite news|title=Prometheus: Film Review |url=http://www.timeout.com/london/film/prometheus |first=Tom |last=Huddleston |publisher=Time Out | work=Time Out London |date=2012-05-31 |accessdate=2013-12-28 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130622114417/http://www.timeout.com/london/film/prometheus |archivedate=2013-06-22 |deadurl=no}}</ref>伊曼纽尔·利维（{{lang|en|Emanuel Levy}}）表示，剧本是他对本片唯一感到失望的方面，对此他说：“不仅仅是不平等，而且还作出了超过能力的承诺要提供更多的原创理念和主题。”<ref name="RevLevy">{{cite news |title=Prometheus |url=http://emanuellevy.com/review/prometheus-2/ |first=Emanuel |last=Levy |publisher=Emanuellevy.com |year=2012 |accessdate=2013-12-28 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20120830194723/http://www.emanuellevy.com/review/prometheus-2/ |archivedate=2012-08-30 |deadurl=no}}</ref>[[罗杰·艾伯特|罗杰·艾伯特]]给本片四星的高度评价（最高四星），称赞影片的“剧情完美融合，特效和演员都恰到好处，拍摄手法理智，{{lang|en|3D}}镜头有效而且不致分散观众的注意力。”艾伯特认为拉佩斯的表演“延续表现了西格妮·韦弗在《异形》中开创的优秀女性实力”，还对艾尔巴饰演的简尼克一角性格发展最感兴趣。他还认为剧情中提出的问题最终又不做回答，让这部影片变加有趣，并且与“科幻黄金时代的经典传承”保持一致<ref name="RevEbert">{{cite news | last=Ebert| first=Roger | url=http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/prometheus-2012 | title=PROMETHEUS (R) | work=Chicago Sun-Times | publisher=Sun-Times Media Group | date=2012-06-06 |accessdate=2013-12-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131005010238/http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/prometheus-2012 |archivedate=2013-10-05 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。他之后将本片列入2012年最优秀的电影之一<ref name="RevEbert2">{{cite news|last=Ebert |first=Roger |url=http://www.rogerebert.com/rogers-journal/eberts-top-movies-of-2012 |title=EBERT'S TOP MOVIES OF 2012 |publisher=rogerebert.com |date=2012-12-27 |accessdate=2013-12-28 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20131103170800/http://www.rogerebert.com/rogers-journal/eberts-top-movies-of-2012 |archivedate=2013-11-03 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

《[[全面电影|全面电影]]》（{{lang|en|''Total Film''}}）的乔纳森·克罗克（{{lang|en|Jonathan Crocker}}）称赞电影剧情上成功地将自身与《异形》的神话相结合的同时，又提供了自己的原创构想<ref name="RevTotalFilm">{{cite news|title=Prometheus |url=http://www.totalfilm.com/reviews/cinema/prometheus-1 |first=Jonathan |last=Crocker |work=Total Film |publisher=Future plc |date=2012-05-30 |accessdate=2013-12-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130911003259/http://www.totalfilm.com/reviews/cinema/prometheus-1 |archivedate=2013-09-11 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》的丽莎·施瓦茨鲍姆（{{lang|en|Lisa Schwarzbaum}}）对电影中的演员——特别是拉佩斯——和摄影表现持肯定态度<ref name="RevEW">{{cite news|last=Schwarzbaum |first=Lisa |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20587886,00.html |title=Prometheus (2012) |work=Entertainment Weekly |publisher=Time Inc. |date=2012-06-06 |accessdate=2013-12-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130522202716/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20587886%2C00.html |archivedate=2013-05-22 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[Salon|Salon]]}}网站的安德鲁·奥黑尔（{{lang|en|Andrew O'Hehir}}）称这部电影“阴郁、壮观而沉重”，但其“自命不凡和装腔作势……既是电影的强大实力，又是其极大的弱点”，他还批评片中角色缺乏常识，并谈论了沃尔斯基的摄影和马克思的艺术指导表现<ref name="RevSalon">{{cite news|last=O'Hehir |first=Andrew |url=http://www.salon.com/2012/06/06/prometheus_ridley_scotts_dazzling_dumb_ass_theology/ |title="Prometheus": Ridley Scott’s dazzling, sci-fi spectacle |work=Salon |publisher=Salon Media Group |date=2012-06-06 |accessdate=2013-12-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130330155213/http://www.salon.com/2012/06/06/prometheus_ridley_scotts_dazzling_dumb_ass_theology/ |archivedate=2013-03-30 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》的{{lang|en|[[A·O·斯科特|A·O·斯科特]]}}（{{lang|en|A. O. Scott}}）批评电影剧情弱薄，叙事的曲折和反复削弱了其“高高在上，震撼人心的潜力”。他认为这部电影没有任何的启示，只有“令人吃惊的瞬间中包含的失去意义或共鸣的信息”，不过他还是称赞了拉佩斯饰演的女主角“脆弱而坚定”<ref name="RevNYT">{{cite news | last=Scott | first=A.O. | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/06/08/movies/prometheus-by-ridley-scott-with-noomi-rapace.html?_r=0 | title=Something Wicked Their Way Comes, via the Galactic Void | work=The New York Times | publisher=The New York Times Company | date = 2012-06-07 |accessdate=2013-12-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120813070027/http://www.nytimes.com/2012/06/08/movies/prometheus-by-ridley-scott-with-noomi-rapace.html |archivedate=2012-08-13 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

《[[综艺|综艺]]》[[杂志|杂志]]影评人贾斯汀·常（{{lang|en|Justin Chang}}）认为，这部电影的叙事结构无法处理剧情的哲学思维，并且考虑到很可能会拍摄续集，本片在关键的故事情节上就懒散地进行了延迟<ref name="RevVariety">{{cite news |title=Prometheus |url=http://variety.com/2012/film/reviews/prometheus-1117947665/ |first=Justin |last=Chang |work=Variety |publisher=PMC |date=2012-05-30 |accessdate=2013-12-28 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131217204911/http://variety.com/2012/film/reviews/prometheus-1117947665/ | archivedate = 2013-12-17 | deadurl=no}}</ref>。《[[卫报|卫报]]》的彼得·布拉德肖（{{lang|en|Peter Bradshaw}}）认为《普罗米修斯》与《异形》相比“更宏伟，更详细”但在引起观众兴趣上则有所不足，缺乏“临门一脚”<ref name="RevGuardian">{{cite news |title=Prometheus – review |url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2012/may/30/prometheus-review |first1=Peter |last1=Bradshaw |work=The Guardian |publisher=Guardian Media Group |date=2012-05-30 |accessdate=2013-12-28 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68Ucrqlio?url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2012/may/30/prometheus-review |archivedate=2012-06-17 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。《[[帝国杂志|帝国杂志]]》的伊恩·内森（{{lang|en|Ian Nathan}}）对拉佩斯的角色不以为然，觉得这个主角缺乏说服力。他认为这部电影“缺乏悬念，角色俗套，剧本单薄。虽然有令人惊叹的视觉效果和法斯賓達的精彩表演，也没能避免《普罗米修斯》感觉起来就像是《异形》的穷亲戚”<ref name="RevEmpire">{{cite news|first=Ian |last=Nathan |title=Prometheus |url=http://www.empireonline.com/reviews/reviewcomplete.asp?FID=137119 |work=Empire |publisher=Bauer Media Group |year=2012 |accessdate=2013-12-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131101195627/http://www.empireonline.com/reviews/reviewcomplete.asp?FID=137119 |archivedate=2013-11-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。《[[乡村之声|乡村之声]]》（{{lang|en|''The Village Voice''}}）的尼克·平克顿（{{lang|en|Nick Pinkerton}}）认为《普罗米修斯》是一部“容易显得浅薄而沉重”的电影，而斯科特“仍然能够把一部史诗般高贵和重要的电影外表模仿得似模像样——但这样的电影也就只剩下外表而已。”他批评拉佩斯和马歇尔·格林没能让两人角色间的恋情引起观众的兴趣，不过也称片中还是有一些能够引起爱好者兴趣并加以收藏的东西<ref name="RevVillageVoice">{{cite news | last=Pinkerton | first=Nick | url=http://www.villagevoice.com/2012-06-06/film/prometheus-ridley-scott/ | title=Prometheus: The Tree of Death | work=The Village Voice | publisher=Village Voice Media | date=2012-06-06 |accessdate=2013-12-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131108012443/http://www.villagevoice.com/2012-06-06/film/prometheus-ridley-scott/ |archivedate=2013-11-08 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

詹姆斯·卡梅隆表示：“我喜欢《普罗米修斯》，这部电影真是棒极了。我认为这是雷德利对科幻电影极具兴致的回归，拥有优异的战术性能，漂亮的摄师和杰出的原生{{lang|en|3D}}。可能会有一些地方我会用不同的方式处理，但这并不重要，因为对于任何电影你都可以这样说。”<ref name="Cameron">{{cite web |archivedate=2013-12-28 |deadurl=yes |url=http://news.moviefone.com/2012/09/06/james-cameron-titanic-kat/ |title=James Cameron On Kate Winslet's 'Titanic' Comments: 'Get Over It' |last=Heynman |first=Jessie |work=news.moviefone.com |date=2012-09-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131228071222/http://news.moviefone.com/2012/09/06/james-cameron-titanic-kat/ |accessdate=2013-12-28 }}</ref>

