2012年6月1日，《普罗米修斯》的{{lang|en|[[DVD|DVD]]}}和[[蓝光影碟|蓝光影碟]]出现在[[亚马逊公司|亚马逊公司]]的预订商品名单上，这时距其在影院上映都还有一个礼拜。还有提供有限的电影票来作为预订的奖励措施<ref name="HomeBRay1">{{cite news|first=Josh |last=Katz |url=http://www.blu-ray.com/news/?id=8839 |title=Prometheus Blu-ray, Pre-Order and Get One Movie Ticket |publisher=Blu-ray.com |date=2012-06-01 |accessdate=2013-12-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130602175522/http://www.blu-ray.com/news/?id=8839 |archivedate=2013-06-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。2012年6月，{{lang|en|[[FX_(电视频道)|FX]]}}获得了影片的网络电视首映权<ref name="HomeMedia4">{{cite news | url=http://www.deadline.com/2012/06/prometheus-fx-television-rights-fox/ | title=FX Acquires ‘Prometheus’ TV Rights | publisher=PMC |work=Deadline.com | date=2012-06-11 | accessdate=2013-12-27 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121012010216/http://www.deadline.com/2012/06/prometheus-fx-television-rights-fox/ |archivedate=2012-10-12 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。2012年9月7日，福克斯宣布《普罗米修斯》将成为其新数字发布平台“数字{{lang|en|HD}}”（{{lang|en|Digital HD}}）的首发作品。影片于2012年9月18日开始通过包括亚马逊、{{lang|en|iTunes}}、{{lang|en|[[PlayStation_Network|PlayStation Network]]}}和{{lang|en|[[Xbox_Live|Xbox Live]]}}以内的多个平台在超过50个国家进行下载和流媒体发行，比{{lang|en|DVD}}、蓝光影碟和[[隨選視訊|隨選視訊]]还要早三个星期<ref name="HomeDigital">{{cite news | first=David | last=Lieberman | url=http://www.deadline.com/2012/09/fox-digital-hd-movie-download/ | title=Fox Hopes To Boost Movie Downloads By Offering Titles Ahead Of Discs | publisher=PMC |work=Deadline.com | date=2012-09-07 | accessdate=2013-12-27 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121014112937/http://www.deadline.com/2012/09/fox-digital-hd-movie-download |archivedate=2012-10-14 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。影片的{{lang|en|DVD}}和蓝光影碟于2012年10月9日发布<ref name="HomeMedia2">{{cite web|title=Prometheus Blu-ray |archivedate=2013-10-31 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131031211313/http://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Prometheus-Blu-ray/39475/ |url=http://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Prometheus-Blu-ray/39475/ |publisher=Blu-ray.com |year=2012 |accessdate=2013-12-27 }}</ref>。电影的蓝光影碟分为一个双碟套装和一个四碟的“珍藏版”。两者都包括影院上映版本的《普罗米修斯》，斯科特、林道夫和斯派茨的评论音轨，电影的{{lang|en|DVD}}和数字副本，替代和删除镜头以及其他花絮。此外珍藏版还包含电影的3D版本以及包括电影制作纪录片在内长近7个小时的附加花絮<ref name="HomeMedia5">{{cite web|first= Adam|last=Chitwood |title=Prometheus Blu-ray Trailer Promises Questions Will Be Answered; Ridley Scott Says Social Network Convinced Him to Shoot on RED |url=http://collider.com/prometheus-blu-ray-trailer/198729/ | publisher=Collider.com |date=2012-09-28 |accessdate=2013-12-27 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131006104849/http://collider.com/prometheus-blu-ray-trailer/198729/ |archivedate=2013-10-06 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。2012年10月8日，有报道称福克斯要求为家用媒体制作本片的加长版，但斯科特拒绝把已经删减的镜头又加回到影院版本的电影中，他认为电影院上映的就相当于是自己的导演剪辑版<ref name="HomeMedia10" />。《普罗米修斯》的{{lang|en|DVD}}和蓝光影碟在英国发行首周就登上畅销榜冠军定座，并且与亚军的销量相较的比例为三比一<ref name="HomeUK1">{{cite web|first=Dan |last=Lane |title=Alien prequel Prometheus tops Official Video Chart |url=http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/alien-prequel-prometheus-tops-official-video-chart-1645/ |publisher=Official Charts Company |date=2012-10-15 |accessdate=2013-12-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130313143539/http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/alien-prequel-prometheus-tops-official-video-chart-1645/ |archivedate=2013-03-13 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

== 续集 ==
{{main|异形：圣约}}
在2012年3月17日的{{lang|en|WonderCon}}展会上，斯科特表示本片留下许多尚未解决的问题，可能会在续集解答。他说：“如果我们运气好的话，会有第二部出来。影片的确留给了你一些很好的悬而未决的问题。”<ref name="Sequel2" /><ref name="Sequel1" />。面对续集是否会是《异形》直接相关前传的问题，林道夫回答：“如果我们有幸制作续集的话……它会和原本的《异形》距离更远。”<ref name="MiscWonderCon12" />2012年6月，林道夫称本片中有些剧情元素是故意让其没有得到解决，以便在续集中给出答案，他和斯科特已经深入讨论了解决方案，使《普罗米修斯》即使没有续集也可以成为一部独立的作品<ref name="Sequel4">{{cite news | last=Gilchrist | first=Todd | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/prometheus-damon-lindelof-sequel-ridley-scott-paradise-332875 | title='Prometheus' Writer Damon Lindelof on Rumored Sequel 'Paradise' and Whether He's the Man to Write It | publisher=Prometheus Global Media | work=The Hollywood Reporter | date=2012-06-05 |accessdate=2013-12-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130325080544/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/prometheus-damon-lindelof-sequel-ridley-scott-paradise-332875 |archivedate=2013-03-25 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。斯科特称，续集将跟随肖前往她的下一个目的地：“因为要是那就是天堂，天堂就不可能是你所想像的那个样子。天堂的内涵是极端险恶和不详的。”林道夫觉得自己有可能不会参与续集的制作，但他也表示，如果斯科特希望某个项目有他的参与，那他会很难拒绝。同时他还认为《普罗米修斯》有从新鲜的构思或创意中获益<ref name="Sequel6">{{cite web |first= Adam |last=Chitwood |title=Prometheus Sequel Recap: What We Know About the Possible Follow-Up So Far |url=http://collider.com/prometheus-2-sequel/172444/ | publisher=Collider.com |date=2012-06-11 |accessdate=2013-12-26 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131111065706/http://collider.com/prometheus-2-sequel/172444/ |archivedate=2013-11-11 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。斯科特表示，还需要有一部额外的电影来弥合《普罗米修斯》的续集和《异形》之间存在的差距<ref name="Sequel7">{{cite web|url=http://downloads.bbc.co.uk/podcasts/fivelive/kermode/kermode_20120601-1008a.mp3 |title=Sir Ridley Scott, 01 June 12 |author=Scott, Ridley |publisher=BBC Online |quote=Yeah, it's not the same planet at all. No. If there was a sequel to this, which there might be if the film is successful, there'll be two more of these before you even get to ''Alien 1''. |date=2012-06-01 |accessdate=2013-12-26 |archivedate=2013-11-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131110183808/http://downloads.bbc.co.uk/podcasts/fivelive/kermode/kermode_20120601-1008a.mp3 }}</ref>。2012年8月1日，有报道确认福克斯公司打算拍摄续集，斯科特、拉佩斯和法斯賓達都将回归，并且已经在于新的编剧进行商谈，以便在林道夫不能回归时加以接替。影片预计至少要到2014年才会上映<ref name="Sequel8">{{cite news | last=McClintock | first=Pamela | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/summer-movie-franchise-avengers-snow-white-magic-mike-356583 | title=Summer's Studio Smackdown: From 'Men in Black 3' to 'Prometheus,' Which Franchises Will Get Another Chapter | publisher=Prometheus Global Media | work=The Hollywood Reporter | date=2012-08-01 |accessdate=2013-12-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131113165845/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/summer-movie-franchise-avengers-snow-white-magic-mike-356583 |archivedate=2013-11-13 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。2012年12月19日，有报道称林道夫由于已经接下了其他工作而决定不参与本片续集的制作<ref name="SequelDec2012">{{cite web |first= Steve |last=Weintraub |title=Exclusive: Damon Lindelof Is Not Writing the Prometheus Sequel; Explains Why |url=http://collider.com/prometheus-sequel-damon-lindelof/219084/ | publisher=Collider.com |date=2012-12-19 |accessdate=2013-12-26 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131010002355/http://collider.com/prometheus-sequel-damon-lindelof/219084/ | archivedate=2013-10-10 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。2013年6月，有报道称杰克·裴格伦（{{lang|en|Jack Paglen}}）正在进行担任续集编剧的谈判<ref name="SequelJun2013">{{cite news|first=Justin |last=Kroll |url=http://variety.com/2013/film/news/transcendence-scribe-to-pen-prometheus-sequel-1200478483/ |title=‘Prometheus’ Sequel Moving Forward at Fox |publisher=PMC |work=Variety |date=2013-06-17 |accessdate=2013-12-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131115005457/http://variety.com/2013/film/news/transcendence-scribe-to-pen-prometheus-sequel-1200478483/ |archivedate=2013-11-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。2013年10月，斯科特确认剧本已经完成<ref name="SequelOct2013">{{cite news|first=Ann |last=Lee |url=http://metro.co.uk/2013/10/27/ridley-scott-confirms-prometheus-2-is-still-on-the-way-4162956/ |title=Ridley Scott confirms Prometheus 2 is still on the way |publisher=dmg media |work=Metro |date=2013-10-27 |accessdate=2013-12-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131030054538/http://metro.co.uk/2013/10/27/ridley-scott-confirms-prometheus-2-is-still-on-the-way-4162956/ |archivedate=2013-10-30 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="SequelOct2013B">{{cite web|first=Hugh |last=Armitage |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/news/a527586/prometheus-2-script-is-finished-says-ridley-scott.html |title='Prometheus 2' script is finished, says Ridley Scott |publisher=Hearst Corporation |work=Digital Spy |date=2013-10-30 |accessdate=2013-12-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131101174908/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/news/a527586/prometheus-2-script-is-finished-says-ridley-scott.html |archivedate=2013-11-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。但在2014年3月，却有报道称迈克尔·格林（{{lang|en|Michael Green}}）正受聘重写裴格伦的剧本<ref>{{cite news|first=Jeff |last=Sneider |url=http://www.thewrap.com/prometheus-2-lands-green-lantern-writer-may-feature-multiple-michael-fassbenders-exclusive/ |title=‘Prometheus 2' Lands ‘Green Lantern’ Writer; May Feature Multiple Michael Fassbenders (Exclusive) |publisher=The Wrap |date=2014-03-24 |accessdate=2014-03-24 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140324235825/http://www.thewrap.com/prometheus-2-lands-green-lantern-writer-may-feature-multiple-michael-fassbenders-exclusive/ |archivedate=2014-03-24 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=Adam |last=Chitwood |title=Ridley Scott To Next Direct Prometheus Sequel For March 4, 2016 Release; Filming Begins This Fall |url=http://collider.com/prometheus-2-release-date/ |publisher=Collider.com |work= |date=2014-03-24 |accessdate=2014-03-24 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140324235948/http://collider.com/prometheus-2-release-date/ |archivedate=2014-03-24 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。影片于2017年5月19日上映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/alien-covenant-release-date-ridley-scott-1201717409/ |title=Ridley Scott’s ‘Alien: Covenant’ Moved Up to Summer 2017 |publisher=Variety |last=McNary |first=Dave |date=2016-02-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160412123507/http://variety.com/2016/film/news/alien-covenant-release-date-ridley-scott-1201717409/ |archivedate=2016-04-12 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

